text: Van Wert is a city in and the county seat of Van Wert County, Ohio, United States. The city is in northwestern Ohio about 77 mi (123 km) SW of Toledo and 34 mi (54 km) SE of Fort Wayne, Indiana. The population was 11,092 at the 2020 census. == References == Category:Cities in Ohio Category:County seats in Ohio
